oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Pee Wee King, Redd Stewart, and the Collins Sisters
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Collins Sisters; Harry (Hap) Peebles Agency; King, Pee Wee, 1914-2000; Offset printing; Stewart, Redd; Western, Johnny;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color offset printing plate (blue on silver) advertising Grand Ole Opry stars Pee Wee King, Redd Stwart, the Collins Sisters (Darlene and Joyce), and Johnny Western, available through the Harry (Hap) Peebles Agency. The plate features photographs of Pee Wee King, Redd Stewart, the Collins Sisters, and Johnny Western.
